Class ProjectLocation

java.lang.Object
src.model.ProjectLocation
public class ProjectLocation extends Object
Represents the geographical location of a project, including district, town, address, and coordinates.

  • Constructor Details

    • ProjectLocation

      public ProjectLocation(int locationId, String district, String town, String address, double lat, double lng)
      Constructs a new ProjectLocation with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      locationId - Unique identifier for this location.
      district - Administrative district (e.g., North, Central).
      town - Town or planning area (e.g., Yishun, Clementi).
      address - Street-level address.
      lat - Latitude coordinate.
      lng - Longitude coordinate.
